title: StarTalk Live! from SF Sketchfest 2015
description: Explore the Moon, asteroids and Mars from the stage of San Francisco’s Nourse Theater with Bill Nye, Eugene Mirman and guests astrophysicist Dr. Yvonne Pendleton, “Mars Czar” Dr. G. Scott Hubbard and comedian H. Jon Benjamin.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
